snippet.title: PlayStation All-Stars Battle Royale - Kat Trailer
snippet.description:
PlayStation® All-Stars Battle Royale™ is free-for-all brawler featuring the greatest stars in the PlayStation universe! Take control of Gravity Rush's Kat and her mysterious feline companion Dusty to turn the fight upside down.

http://www.playstationallstars.com
